# Eval-harness output. Each `bun run harness/run.ts ...` writes a fresh
# `runs/<timestamp>/` with paired trace JSONLs + stdout/stderr captures.
# Reproducible by re-running against the same fixture; not source of truth.
# `git add -f runs/<dir>/` if a specific run needs to be persisted as
# evidence for a finding (see SMOKE-FINDINGS.md's verification table).
runs/
